#. module: campsite
#: model_terms:product.template,description_ecommerce:campsite.product_template_3
msgid ""
"A cozy spot for your tent or small camper, tucked away in the heart of the "
"forest or bathed in sunlight in a peaceful clearing. Perfect for an "
"intimate, close-to-nature getaway."
msgstr ""
"A cozy spot for your tent or small camper, tucked away in the heart of the "
"forest or bathed in sunlight in a peaceful clearing. Perfect for an "
"intimate, close-to-nature getaway."

#. module: campsite
#: model:product.template,name:campsite.product_template_19
msgid "AA Batteries (4)"
msgstr "Baterai AA (4)"

#. module: campsite
#: model:product.template,name:campsite.product_template_20
msgid "AAA Batteries (4)"
msgstr "Baterai AAA (4)"

#. module: campsite
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:campsite.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Access the rates from the same menu to see how price rules apply during the "
"year."
msgstr ""
"Akses tarif dari menu yang sama untuk melihat penerapan peraturan harga "
"sepanjang tahun."

#. module: campsite
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:campsite.welcome_article_body
msgid "Access to more details clicking the slot."
msgstr "Klik slot ini untuk melihat detail lengkapnya."

#. module: campsite
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:campsite.welcome_article_body
msgid "Add a line with Plancha or a Fan."
msgstr "Tambahkan baris dengan Plancha atau Kipas."

#. module: campsite
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:campsite.welcome_article_body
msgid "Add here as many of them as needed."
msgstr "Tambahkan di sini sebanyak mungkin yang dibutuhkan."

#. module: campsite
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:campsite.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Add some products to the ongoing order and send it to the preparation "
"display and\n"
"                bring them to your guests."
msgstr ""
"Tambahkan beberapa produk ke pesanan yang sedang berjalan dan kirimkan ke "
"layar persiapan, lalu\n"
"                sajikan kepada tamu Anda."

#. module: campsite
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:campsite.welcome_article_body
msgid "Adjust the number of stars, leave a comment and send it!"
msgstr "Sesuaikan jumlah bintang, beri komentar, lalu kirimkan!"

#. module: campsite
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:campsite.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Adjust the rental dates, click the book button and then proceed to checkout."
msgstr ""
"Sesuaikan tanggal rental, klik tombol \"pesan\", lalu lanjutkan ke checkout."

#. module: campsite
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:campsite.welcome_article_body
msgid "Adjust your prices along the year"
msgstr "Menyesuaikan harga seiring berjalannya tahun"

#. module: campsite
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:campsite.welcome_article_body
msgid "Adjusting your offers in consequence"
msgstr "Menyesuaikan penawaran secara berkala"

#. module: campsite
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:campsite.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Again, the <strong>Campsite App </strong>helps you manage the end of the "
"stay!"
msgstr ""
"Sekali lagi, <strong>Aplikasi Campsite </strong>membantu Anda mengelola "
"akhir masa inap!"

#. module: campsite
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:campsite.custom_product_name
msgid "All Stay Offers"
msgstr "Semua Penawaran Menginap"

#. module: campsite
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:campsite.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Alternativelly, you can use the Front Desk from the POS App, selecting the\n"
"                    customer, adding any additional services and then paying "
"with the customer\n"
"                    account. At the end of the stay the customer account "
"will be charged as well."
msgstr ""
"Anda juga bisa menggunakan Front Desk dari Aplikasi POS, pilih\n"
"                    pelanggan, tambahkan layanan tambahannya, lalu bayar "
"menggunakan akun\n"
"                    pelanggan. Pada akhir periode menginap, akun pelanggan "
"juga akan ditagih."

#. module: campsite
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:campsite.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Alternatively to individual resource blocking slots described earlier, you "
"can select a resource this leave applies to."
msgstr ""
"Selain slot blocking sumber daya satuan yang dijelaskan sebelumnya, Anda "
"dapat memilih sumber daya yang berlaku untuk cuti ini."

#. module: campsite
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:campsite.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Alternatively, switch to the list view, and then change the resource.<br/"
">Be\n"
"                    careful not to double book a resource with such change!"
msgstr ""
"Anda juga bisa beralih ke tampilan daftar, lalu mengubah sumber dayanya.<br/"
">Berhati-hatilah\n"
"                    agar tidak memesan sumber daya dua kali dengan perubahan "
"tersebut!"

#. module: campsite
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:campsite.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Alternatively, switch to the list view, which is more suitable if the "
"booking is\n"
"                    not during the visualized date range and update the "
"booking date range."
msgstr ""
"Anda juga bisa beralih ke tampilan daftar, yang lebih cocok jika pemesanan\n"
"                    tidak dalam rentang tanggal yang ditampilkan, dan "
"memperbarui rentang tanggal pemesanan."

#. module: campsite
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:campsite.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Alternatively, type in the search bar and select the appropriate filter."
msgstr "Atau, ketik di kolom pencarian dan pilih filter yang sesuai."

#. module: campsite
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:campsite.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Alternatively, you can create a slot as placeholder from the planning "
"directly:"
msgstr ""
"Anda juga dapat membuat slot sebagai placeholder langsung dari perencanaan:"

#. module: campsite
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:campsite.welcome_article_body
msgid "An automation is setup for an email to be sent automatically for you."
msgstr ""
"Sistem otomatisasi telah disiapkan agar email dikirimkan secara otomatis "
"untuk Anda."

#. module: campsite
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:campsite.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Any time you create a new survey and save it with the setting \"is customer "
"satisfaction survey\", previous ones\n"
"                    will be archived so that it becomes your new default "
"survey."
msgstr ""
"Setiap kali Anda membuat survei baru dan menyimpannya dengan pengaturan "
"\"adalah survei kepuasan pelanggan\", survei sebelumnya\n"
"                    akan diarsipkan sehingga menjadi survei default yang "
"baru."

#. module: campsite
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:campsite.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Anyone can create a portal account on your database.<br/>Open your website "
"home page\n"
"                in a private tab to do so."
msgstr ""
"Siapa pun dapat membuat akun portal di database Anda.<br/>Buka halaman "
"beranda website\n"
"                di tab pribadi untuk melakukannya."

#. module: campsite
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:campsite.homepage
msgid "Are you considering a tentalo getaway?"
msgstr "Ingin liburan ala glamping dengan tentalo?"

#. module: campsite
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:campsite.welcome_article_body
msgid "Assign them a resource, which helps you keeping track."
msgstr "Tetapkan sumber daya kepadanya untuk membantu pelacakan."

#. module: campsite
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:campsite.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"At any time during their stay, open their rental order from the Campsite App."
msgstr ""
"Kapan pun selama masa menginap, buka rental order tamu dari Aplikasi "
"Campsite."

#. module: campsite
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:campsite.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"At any time from the guest order, use the Send message capability in the "
"chatter\n"
"                    to exchange with your guest."
msgstr ""
"Kapan pun dari pesanan tamu, gunakan fitur Kirim pesan di chatter\n"
"                    untuk berkomunikasi dengan tamu Anda."

#. module: campsite
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:campsite.welcome_article_body
msgid "At the end of their stay, your guests will pay for all those extras."
msgstr ""
"Pada akhir periode inap, tamu Anda akan membayar semua tambahan tersebut."

#. module: campsite
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:campsite.welcome_article_body
msgid "Bar &amp; Restaurant and extra services"
msgstr "Bar &amp; Restoran dan layanan tambahan"

#. module: campsite
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:campsite.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Because keeping an eye on your business performance matter, the module comes "
"with a dedicated dashboard."
msgstr ""

#. module: campsite
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:campsite.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Beyond daily operations, the Steering menu serves as the \"Captain’s "
"Bridge\" of your campsite. It provides a 500-day horizon to anticipate "
"market trends, manage risks, and optimize your revenue."
msgstr ""
"Selain operasional sehari-hari, menu Steering berfungsi sebagai \"Pusat "
"Kendali\" campsite Anda. Fitur ini memberikan insight 500 hari ke depan "
"untuk mengantisipasi tren pasar, mengelola risiko, dan mengoptimalkan "
"pendapatan Anda."

#. module: campsite
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:campsite.welcome_article_body
msgid "Blocking resources"
msgstr "Blocking sumber daya"

#. module: campsite
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:campsite.welcome_article_body
msgid "Booking a pitch"
msgstr "Memesan lahan kemah"

#. module: campsite
#: model:product.template,name:campsite.product_template_17
msgid "Bread"
msgstr "Roti"

#. module: campsite
#: model:product.category,name:campsite.product_category_8
#: model:product.public.category,name:campsite.product_public_category_9
msgid "Bungalows"
msgstr "Bungalow"

#. module: campsite
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:campsite.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"By uploading this module's demo data, your database has been filled with a "
"few products,\n"
"            sale orders and more."
msgstr ""
"Dengan mengunggah data demo modul ini, database Anda telah diisi dengan "
"beberapa produk,\n"
"            sales order, dan lainnya."

#. module: campsite
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:campsite.res_config_settings_form_view_inherited
msgid "Campsite"
msgstr "Campsite"

#. module: campsite
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:campsite.homepage
msgid "Carousel Indicator"
msgstr "Indikator Carousel"

#. module: campsite
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:campsite.welcome_article_body
msgid "Charge your guests"
msgstr "Membuat tagihan untuk tamu"

#. module: campsite
#: model_terms:product.template,description_ecommerce:campsite.product_template_6
msgid ""
"Charming and compact, these A-frame cabins blend rustic style with modern "
"convenience. A snug retreat for couples or solo travelers looking for a "
"warm, sheltered stay in nature."
msgstr ""
"Charming and compact, these A-frame cabins blend rustic style with modern "
"convenience. A snug retreat for couples or solo travelers looking for a "
"warm, sheltered stay in nature."

#. module: campsite
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:campsite.homepage
msgid "Check Out Out Stay Offers"
msgstr "Lihat Penawaran Menginap Kami"

#. module: campsite
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:campsite.welcome_article_body
msgid "Check guests in"
msgstr "Melakukan check-in tamu"

#. module: campsite
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:campsite.welcome_article_body
msgid "Check guests out"
msgstr "Melakukan check-out tamu"

#. module: campsite
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:campsite.welcome_article_body
msgid "Check information and then confirm the booking."
msgstr "Periksa informasi, lalu konfirmasi pemesanan."

#. module: campsite
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:campsite.welcome_article_body
msgid "Click one of the offers to book."
msgstr "Klik salah satu penawaran yang akan dipesan."

#. module: campsite
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:campsite.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Click the Check in button to confirm they are now staying at your place!"
msgstr ""
"Klik tombol Check in untuk mengonfirmasi bahwa tamu kini menginap di tempat "
"Anda!"

#. module: campsite
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:campsite.welcome_article_body
msgid "Click the Check out button to capture they left their spot ."
msgstr ""
