#. module: campsite
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:campsite.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Open the <strong>Settings App</strong> and reach the companies from the menu "
"Users &amp; Companies."
msgstr ""
"Buka <strong>Aplikasi Pengaturan</strong> dan akses perusahaan melalui menu "
"User &amp; Perusahaan."

#. module: campsite
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:campsite.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Open the <strong>Settings App</strong> and reach the users from the menu "
"Users &amp; Companies."
msgstr ""
"Buka <strong>Aplikasi Pengaturan</strong> dan akses user melalui menu User "
"&amp; Perusahaan."

#. module: campsite
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:campsite.welcome_article_body
msgid "Open the <strong>Website App</strong> and navigate to the Stay Offers."
msgstr ""
"Buka <strong>Aplikasi Website</strong> dan buka bagian Penawaran Menginap."

#. module: campsite
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:campsite.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Open the Board from the accommodation app, House Keeping menu.<br/>Here you "
"have an\n"
"                overview of the cleanness state of your resources."
msgstr ""
"Buka Papan dari aplikasi akomodasi, menu House Keeping.<br/>Di sini, ada\n"
"                gambaran umum tentang kondisi kebersihan sumber daya Anda."

#. module: campsite
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:campsite.welcome_article_body
msgid "Open the Campsite App and navigate to the Configuration / Leaves menu."
msgstr "Buka Aplikasi Campsite dan buka menu Konfigurasi / Cuti."

#. module: campsite
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:campsite.welcome_article_body
msgid "Open the Campsite App and then navigate to the orders from the menu."
msgstr "Buka Aplikasi Campsite, lalu buka bagian pesanan dari menu."

#. module: campsite
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:campsite.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Open the Campsite App to appreciate the currently planned bookings with the\n"
"                Schedule."
msgstr ""
"Buka Aplikasi Campsite untuk melihat pemesanan yang sedang direncanakan "
"melalui\n"
"                Jadwal."

#. module: campsite
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:campsite.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Open the Default pricelist to see the existing price rules which apply to it."
msgstr ""
"Buka daftar harga Default untuk melihat peraturan harga yang berlaku "
"untuknya."

#. module: campsite
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:campsite.welcome_article_body
msgid "Open the POS App and select one of the register, the Bar for example."
msgstr "Buka Aplikasi POS dan pilih salah satu kasir, misalnya Bar."

#. module: campsite
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:campsite.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Open the Pricelists from the <strong>Campsite App</strong>, Configuration / "
"Pricelists menu."
msgstr ""
"Buka Daftar Harga dari menu Konfigurasi / Daftar Harga di <strong>Aplikasi "
"Campsite</strong>."

#. module: campsite
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:campsite.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Open the Settings App and navigate to the Rental section or search for "
"\"Unavailability days\"."
msgstr ""
"Buka Aplikasi Pengaturan dan buka bagian Rental atau cari \"Hari yang tidak "
"tersedia\"."

#. module: campsite
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:campsite.welcome_article_body
msgid "Open the Steering menu and select Availability."
msgstr "Buka menu Steering dan pilih Ketersediaan."

#. module: campsite
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:campsite.welcome_article_body
msgid "Open the Steering menu and select Occupancy."
msgstr "Buka menu Steering dan pilih Okupansi."

#. module: campsite
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:campsite.welcome_article_body
msgid "Open the Survey App to find the customer satisfaction survey."
msgstr "Buka Aplikasi Survei untuk mengakses survei kepuasan pelanggan."

#. module: campsite
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:campsite.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Open the door for more custom workflows and actions with the power of "
"<strong>Studio\n"
"                App</strong>."
msgstr ""
"Bukakan peluang untuk alur kerja dan tindakan yang lebih spesifik dengan "
"kebutuhan Anda bersama <strong>Aplikasi\n"
"                Studio</strong>."

#. module: campsite
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:campsite.welcome_article_body
msgid "Open the order of you just arrived guests."
msgstr "Buka pesanan tamu yang baru saja tiba."

#. module: campsite
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:campsite.welcome_article_body
msgid "Open your guest order from the Campsite App."
msgstr "Buka pesanan tamu dari Aplikasi Campsite."

#. module: campsite
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:campsite.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Optimizing weekly turnover to maximize occupancy during peak season, you can "
"align your bookings to a weekly rental pattern (e.g., Saturday to Saturday). "
"By restricting check-ins and check-outs to specific days, you synchronize "
"your housekeeping and eliminate calendar gaps."
msgstr ""
"Untuk mengoptimalkan pergantian tamu mingguan guna memaksimalkan okupansi "
"selama peak season, Anda dapat menyesuaikan pemesanan dengan pola rental "
"mingguan (misalnya, Sabtu ke Sabtu). Dengan membatasi waktu check-in dan "
"check-out pada hari-hari tertentu, Anda dapat menyinkronkan housekeeping dan "
"menghilangkan celah dalam kalender."

#. module: campsite
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:campsite.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Organize your employees' schedules with<font class=\"text-o-color-5\"> "
"<strong>\n"
"                Planning</strong></font><strong>\n"
"                    <font class=\"text-o-color-5\"> App</font>\n"
"                </strong><font class=\"text-o-color-5\">.</font>"
msgstr ""
"Atur jadwal karyawan Anda dengan<font class=\"text-o-color-5\"> <strong>\n"
"                Aplikasi</strong></font><strong>\n"
"                    <font class=\"text-o-color-5\"> Perencanaan.</font>\n"
"                </strong><font class=\"text-o-color-5\"></font>"

#. module: campsite
#: model:product.category,name:campsite.product_category_6
#: model:product.public.category,name:campsite.product_public_category_11
msgid "Pitches"
msgstr "Lapangan"

#. module: campsite
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:campsite.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Plan, check in and and check out bookings with the <strong>Campsite App</"
"strong>"
msgstr ""
"Lakukan perencanaan, check-in, dan check-out pemesanan dengan "
"<strong>Aplikasi Campsite</strong>"

#. module: campsite
#: model:product.template,name:campsite.product_template_8
msgid "Plancha"
msgstr "Pemanggang"

#. module: campsite
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:campsite.homepage
msgid "Previous"
msgstr "Sebelum"

#. module: campsite
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:campsite.welcome_article_body
msgid "Proceed to the payment with your terminal and set the invoice as paid."
msgstr ""
"Lanjutkan ke pembayaran dengan terminal Anda dan ubah status faktur sebagai "
"dibayar."

#. module: campsite
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:campsite.welcome_article_body
msgid "Promote your offers through the <strong>Website App</strong>"
msgstr "Promosikan penawaran Anda melalui <strong>Aplikasi Website</strong>"

#. module: campsite
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:campsite.welcome_article_body
msgid "Reach us"
msgstr "Hubungi kami"

#. module: campsite
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:campsite.welcome_article_body
msgid "Record guest identity"
msgstr "Mencatat identitas tamu"

#. module: campsite
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:campsite.welcome_article_body
msgid "Recording the guest attendance is an obligation in numerous countries."
msgstr "Pencatatan kehadiran tamu merupakan kewajiban di banyak negara."

#. module: campsite
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:campsite.welcome_article_body
msgid "Save the order with those extra services."
msgstr "Simpan pesanan dengan layanan tambahan tersebut."

#. module: campsite
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:campsite.homepage
msgid "See All"
msgstr "Lihat Semua"

#. module: campsite
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:campsite.homepage
msgid "See all<span class=\"fa fa-long-arrow-right ms-2\"/>"
msgstr "Lihat semua<span class=\"fa fa-long-arrow-right ms-2\"/>"

#. module: campsite
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:campsite.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"See that for demo purpose we setup typical uplift and discount rules to "
"adjust your prices during key periods."
msgstr ""
"Perhatikan bahwa untuk keperluan demo, kami telah menyiapkan aturan kenaikan "
"harga dan diskon standar untuk menyesuaikan harga selama periode-periode "
"penting."

#. module: campsite
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:campsite.welcome_article_body
msgid "Select one of your employee."
msgstr "Pilih salah satu karyawan Anda."

#. module: campsite
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:campsite.welcome_article_body
msgid "Select or create a customer and then confirm the booking!"
msgstr "Pilih atau buat pelanggan, lalu konfirmasi pemesanan!"

#. module: campsite
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:campsite.welcome_article_body
msgid "Setup company or branch specific offers when relevant."
msgstr "Siapkan penawaran khusus perusahaan atau cabang jika relevan."

#. module: campsite
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:campsite.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Share your stay offers across your companies and branches (default behavior);"
msgstr ""
"Bagikan penawaran menginap Anda di seluruh perusahaan dan cabang (perilaku "
"default);"

#. module: campsite
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:campsite.welcome_article_body
msgid "Simply open the Dashboard App to land on the Performance dashboard."
msgstr ""

#. module: campsite
#: model:product.template,name:campsite.product_template_6
msgid "Small Bungalow (up to 4 pers.)"
msgstr "Bungalow Kecil (maks 4 orang.)"

#. module: campsite
#: model:product.template,name:campsite.product_template_3
msgid "Small Pitch"
msgstr "Small Pitch"

#. module: campsite
#: model_terms:product.template,description_ecommerce:campsite.product_template_4
msgid ""
"Spacious and comfortable, these pitches welcome bigger tents, caravans, or "
"motorhomes. Set in tranquil forest shade or open clearings, they’re ideal "
"for families or groups seeking extra room to relax."
msgstr ""
"Spacious and comfortable, these pitches welcome bigger tents, caravans, or "
"motorhomes. Set in tranquil forest shade or open clearings, they’re ideal "
"for families or groups seeking extra room to relax."

#. module: campsite
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:campsite.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Still from the Campsite App Schedule, simply drag and drop a booking to "
"another offer, from small pitch to large pitch for example!"
msgstr ""
"Masih dari Jadwal Aplikasi Campsite, cukup seret dan lepas pemesanan ke "
"penawaran lain, misalnya dari lahan kemah kecil ke lahan kemah besar!"

#. module: campsite
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:campsite.welcome_article_body
msgid "Still from their Rental Order, open the Guests tab."
msgstr "Masih dari Rental Order pelanggan, buka tab Tamu."

#. module: campsite
#: model:product.template,name:campsite.product_template_5
msgid "Tentalo"
msgstr "Tentalo"

#. module: campsite
#: model:product.category,name:campsite.product_category_7
#: model:product.public.category,name:campsite.product_public_category_10
msgid "Tentalos"
msgstr "Tentalos"

#. module: campsite
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:campsite.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"The Gantt chart is color-coded to reflect on the availability for you to "
"work on filling in."
msgstr ""
"Bagan Gantt diberi kode warna untuk menunjukkan ketersediaan untuk diisi."

#. module: campsite
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:campsite.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"The Gantt chart is color-coded to reflect on the occupancy, the higher the "
"better."
msgstr ""
"Bagan Gantt diberi kode warna untuk mencerminkan status okupansi; makin "
"tinggi, makin baik."

#. module: campsite
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:campsite.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"The Occupancy view allows you to visualize your \"Sales Success\". It "
"answers one simple question: <i>How well am I filling my campsite?</i>"
msgstr ""
"Tampilan Okupansi menyajikan visualisasi \"Keberhasilan Sales\" Anda. "
"Tampilan ini menjawab satu pertanyaan sederhana: <i>Seberapa baik tingkat "
"hunian campsite saya?</i>"

#. module: campsite
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:campsite.homepage
msgid ""
"The feeling of freedom with the comfort of a cabin!<br/>We'll guide you "
"through the options and help you choose the perfect fit for your getaway. "
"<br/> You can decide freely whether to proceed with your booking."
msgstr ""
"Kebebasan akan didapatkan dari nyamannya kabin!<br/>Kami akan memandu Anda "
"melihat-lihat berbagai opsi dan memilih yang paling pas untuk liburan Anda. "
"<br/> Anda bebas memutuskan apakah akan melanjutkan pemesanan atau tidak."

#. module: campsite
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:campsite.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"The strength of Odoo is to separate the accounting and many other aspects "
"which are company dependent!"
msgstr ""
"Keunggulan Odoo adalah memisahkan akuntansi dan aspek-aspek lainnya yang "
"bergantung pada perusahaan!"

#. module: campsite
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:campsite.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Then set the days during which you want to prevent check in and check out to "
"take place, ex. All days but Saturday"
msgstr ""
"Kemudian, tentukan hari yang tidak bisa check-in dan check-out , misalnya: "
"Semua hari kecuali Sabtu"

#. module: campsite
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:campsite.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"These all go free in your current subscription; feel free to explore! 🙃"
msgstr ""
"Semua ini bisa Anda akses gratis dengan langgananmu saat ini. Jangan ragu "
"untuk menjelajahinya! 🙃"

#. module: campsite
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:campsite.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"They as well share the same pricing, defined at the stay offer level, which "
"has its pros and cons."
msgstr ""
"Harganya juga sama dan ditentukan pada tingkat penawaran inap. Hal ini "
"sendiri memiliki kelebihan dan kekurangan."

#. module: campsite
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:campsite.welcome_article_body
msgid "They want multiple pitches?"
msgstr "Tamu ingin beberapa lahan kemah?"

#. module: campsite
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:campsite.welcome_article_body
msgid "They were happy about their stay, let's ask them to leave a review."
msgstr "Pelanggan senang dengan periode inapnya, mari minta ulasan."

#. module: campsite
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:campsite.welcome_article_body
msgid "They will balance their customer account during the check out!"
msgstr "Mereka akan menyelesaikan pembayaran kamar saat checkout!"

#. module: campsite
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:campsite.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"This blocks simulataneously all resources related to this working schedule "
"during the prescribed period."
msgstr ""
"Hal ini mem-block semua sumber daya yang terkait dengan jadwal kerja ini "
"secara bersamaan selama periode yang ditentukan."

#. module: campsite
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:campsite.welcome_article_body
msgid "This capability is enabled by a setting you can set/unset."
msgstr ""

#. module: campsite
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:campsite.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"This setup is relevant in case of place specific offers or when pricing "
"varies between places."
msgstr ""
"Pengaturan ini relevan untuk penawaran di lokasi tertentu atau ketika harga "
"bervariasi di setiap lokasi."

#. module: campsite
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:campsite.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"This time click the Add to last order button to add this pitch to the "
"booking and\n"
"                voila!"
msgstr ""
"Kali ini, klik tombol \"Tambahkan ke pesanan terakhir\" untuk menambahkan "
"lahan kemah ini ke pemesanan, dan\n"
"                selesai!"

#. module: campsite
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:campsite.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"This time, simply leave a note about the why this is booked and save the "
"slot."
msgstr ""
"Kali ini, cukup buat catatan tentang alasan pemesanan ini dan simpan slotnya."

#. module: campsite
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:campsite.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Those city tax are now due as well as any other additional services consumed "
"during the\n"
"            stay."
msgstr ""
"Pajak kota tersebut kini telah jatuh tempo, begitu pula dengan biaya layanan "
"tambahan lainnya yang dinikmati selama\n"
"            menginap."

#. module: campsite
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:campsite.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"To ensure your guests no longer receive the satisfaction survey, you can "
"easily archive it at any time."
msgstr ""
"Untuk memastikan tamu tidak lagi menerima survei kepuasan, Anda dapat "
"mengarsipkannya kapan saja."

#. module: campsite
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:campsite.welcome_article_body
msgid "Trace guest attendance"
msgstr "Melacak kehadiran tamu"

#. module: campsite
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:campsite.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Two options are now available to you with multiple companies and branches:"
msgstr ""
"Kini tersedia dua opsi bagi Anda dengan beberapa perusahaan dan cabang:"

#. module: campsite
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:campsite.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Type in the customer name in the Schedule search bar filtering by Customer."
msgstr ""
"Ketik nama pelanggan di kolom pencarian Jadwal dengan filter menurut "
"Pelanggan."

#. module: campsite
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:campsite.homepage
msgid ""
"We offer small and large pitches, in the heart of the forest, in clearings "
"and in fields."
msgstr ""
"Kami menyediakan lahan berukuran kecil dan besar, di tengah hutan, di lahan "
"terbuka, dan di lapangan."

#. module: campsite
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:campsite.welcome_article_body
msgid "Welcome your guests as well from the <strong>Campsite App</strong>."
msgstr "Sambut juga tamu Anda melalui <strong>Aplikasi Campsite</strong>."

#. module: campsite
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:campsite.welcome_article_body
msgid "When all is in order, confirm their invoice for payment."
msgstr "Setelah semuanya beres, konfirmasikan faktur untuk pembayaran."

#. module: campsite
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:campsite.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"When creating an offer, assign them a company or a branch.<br/>As a result, "
"they are available only for the selected company or branch, and will be "
"available only from its website."
msgstr ""
"Saat membuat penawaran, tetapkan ke perusahaan atau cabang.<br/>Dengan "
"begitu, penawaran tersebut hanya tersedia untuk perusahaan atau cabang yang "
"dipilih, dan hanya dapat diakses melalui website-nya."

#. module: campsite
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:campsite.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"When they ask for the bill, you can charge them directly or add the bill to "
"their\n"
"                customer account.<br/>To do so, open the corresponding order "
"from the table or from\n"
"                the order list and select the customer to charge.<br/>Click "
"the payment and the\n"
"                validation buttons!"
msgstr ""
"Ketika pelanggan meminta tagihan, Anda dapat menagihnya langsung atau "
"menambahkan tagihan ke\n"
"                akun pelanggannya.<br/>Untuk melakukannya, buka pesanan yang "
"bersangkutan dari tabel atau dari\n"
"                daftar pesanan dan pilih pelanggan yang akan ditagih.<br/"
">Klik tombol pembayaran dan\n"
"                tombol validasi!"

#. module: campsite
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:campsite.homepage
msgid "Where every stay becomes a retreat."
msgstr "Ketenangan, di setiap masa inap."

#. module: campsite
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:campsite.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"While Occupancy focuses on what is full, the Availability view focuses on "
"what is left to sell. It is your primary tool for operational safety and "
"\"Scarcity Pricing.\""
msgstr ""
"Sementara Okupansi berfokus pada penuh atau tidaknya kamar, Ketersediaan "
"berfokus pada kamar yang masih bisa dijual. Fitur ini adalah alat utama "
"untuk keamanan operasional dan penetapan \"Harga Kelangkaan\"."

#. module: campsite
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:campsite.welcome_article_body
msgid "Willing to upgrade a booking?"
msgstr "Ingin upgrade pemesanan?"

#. module: campsite
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:campsite.homepage
msgid ""
"With just a click, planning your perfect camping escape has never been "
"simpler.<br/><br/>"
msgstr ""
"Dengan satu klik saja, rencana berkemah Anda jadi lebih sederhana.<br/><br/>"

#. module: campsite
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:campsite.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"With the create slot for this resource, no overlapping booking slot would be "
"created.<br/>Care about the start and end time or this blockage to make to "
"re-open when suited."
msgstr ""
"Dengan slot pembuatan untuk sumber daya ini, slot pemesanan yang tumpang "
"tindih tidak akan terbuat.<br/>Perhatikan waktu mulai dan berakhir atau "
"blocking ini agar dapat dibuka kembali saat diperlukan."

#. module: campsite
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:campsite.welcome_article_body
msgid "Would you like to discuss your Odoo setup with us or go even further?"
msgstr ""
"Apakah Anda ingin mendiskusikan lebih lanjut setup Odoo Anda dengan kami "
"atau melanjutkan tur?"

#. module: campsite
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:campsite.welcome_article_body
msgid "You Campsite is online and future guests found it!"
msgstr "Campsite Anda sudah online dan calon tamu menemukannya!"

#. module: campsite
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:campsite.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"You are repairing a bungalow or simply welcoming family and don't want "
"guests to book it?<br/>Alternatively, you are closing for a week during an "
"inter season break?<br/>Let's have this reflected in your schedule!"
msgstr ""
"Apakah Anda sedang memperbaiki bungalow atau sekadar menjamu keluarga dan "
"tidak ingin tamu memesan akomodasi tersebut?<br/>Atau, apakah Anda akan "
"menutup akomodasi selama seminggu saat jeda antar musim?<br/>Mari sesuaikan "
"hal ini di jadwal Anda!"

#. module: campsite
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:campsite.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"You can access every installed App in your Odoo database on your main "
"dashboard."
msgstr ""
"Semua Aplikasi yang terpasang di database Odoo Anda bisa diakses melalui "
"dasbor utama."

#. module: campsite
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:campsite.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"You can as well select your company and in the Branches tab define branches."
msgstr ""
"Anda juga dapat memilih perusahaan dan mendefinisikan cabang di tab Cabang."

#. module: campsite
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:campsite.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"You can find the participants and answers from the smart buttons of the "
"survey."
msgstr ""
"Peserta dan jawaban dapat ditemukan dengan mengakses tombol cerdas survei."

#. module: campsite
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:campsite.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"You completed that demo use case! There are millions of other ways to adapt "
"your\n"
"                    Odoo setup to fit your business needs."
msgstr ""
"Anda telah berhasil menyelesaikan contoh demo kasus penggunaan ini! Ada "
"banyak cara untuk\n"
"                    menyesuaikan pengaturan Odoo agar sesuai dengan "
"kebutuhan bisnis Anda."

#. module: campsite
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:campsite.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"You could customize this section to add the identity document picture or "
"extra\n"
"                    fields at your convenience with studio. Just be careful, "
"such customizations can\n"
"                    quickly become messy."
msgstr ""
"Anda dapat menyesuaikan bagian ini untuk menambahkan gambar dokumen "
"identitas atau field tambahan\n"
"                    sesuai keinginan dengan studio. Namun, berhati-hatilah, "
"penyesuaian dapat\n"
"                    menjadi berantakan dalam sekejap."

#. module: campsite
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:campsite.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"You didn't import demo data? You can still do it. Go to Apps &gt; Industries "
"&gt;\n"
"                    Upgrade your package and check the related box"
msgstr ""
"Belum mengimpor data demo? Anda masih bisa melakukannya. Buka Aplikasi &gt; "
"Industri &gt;\n"
"                    Upgrade paket Anda dan centang kotak terkait"

#. module: campsite
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:campsite.welcome_article_body
msgid "You have a future guest on the line willing to book a pitch?"
msgstr "Ada calon tamu yang sedang menelepon dan ingin memesan lahan kemah?"

#. module: campsite
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:campsite.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"You have an Campsite but may be providing numerous peripheral services and "
"offers.<br/>Here\n"
"            is how you might centralize those and bind them to your "
"customers in a single database."
msgstr ""
"Selain Campsite, Anda mungkin juga menawarkan berbagai layanan dan penawaran "
"tambahan.<br/>Berikut\n"
"            cara untuk memusatkan semua itu dan menghubungkannya dengan "
"pelanggan dalam satu database."

#. module: campsite
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:campsite.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"You just installed the Odoo for Campsite package. By doing so, we have "
"installed a\n"
"            bunch of necessary apps to run your business efficiently."
msgstr ""
"Anda baru saja menginstal paket Odoo untuk Campsite. Dengan demikian, kami "
"telah menginstal\n"
"            sejumlah aplikasi yang diperlukan untuk menjalankan bisnis Anda "
"secara efisien."

#. module: campsite
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:campsite.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"You may be running multiple places at the same time and most likely be "
"willing to run them all from the same database.<b/>We got you covered with "
"this using multiple companies or branches!"
msgstr ""
"Anda mungkin mengelola beberapa lokasi sekaligus dan ingin mengelola "
"semuanya dari database yang sama.<b/>Kami siap membantu dengan fitur ini "
"untuk mengelola beberapa perusahaan atau cabang!"

#. module: campsite
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:campsite.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"You may have noticed the city tax were added to the guest order from the "
"moment they\n"
"            checked in.<br/>This is because city taxes are to be billed to "
"spent nights in practice\n"
"            and not in theory.<br/>Let's adjust them now."
msgstr ""
"Anda mungkin menyadari bahwa pajak kota telah ditambahkan ke pesanan tamu "
"sejak mereka\n"
"            check-in.<br/>Hal ini dilakukan karena pajak kota harus ditagih "
"berdasarkan jumlah malam aktual,\n"
"            bukan secara teoritis.<br/>Mari sesuaikan sekarang."

#. module: campsite
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:campsite.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"You may want to uplift your margin during high season and be attractive "
"during low one playing on price.<br/>To do so, let's define price rules."
msgstr ""
"Anda mungkin ingin meningkatkan margin selama high season dan menarik "
"pelanggan selama low season dengan memainkan harga.<br/>Untuk melakukannya, "
"mari tentukan peraturan harga."

#. module: campsite
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:campsite.welcome_article_body
msgid "You might have tested this package with or without demo data."
msgstr "Anda mungkin sudah menguji paket ini dengan atau tanpa data demo."

#. module: campsite
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:campsite.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"You noticed that the Identity Check highlights whether you captured all the\n"
"            necessary information for a guest?"
msgstr ""
"Menyadari bahwa Pemeriksaan Identitas menyoroti apakah Anda telah menangkap "
"semua\n"
"            informasi yang diperlukan untuk tamu?"

#. module: campsite
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:campsite.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"You now know how to create a new order.<br/>Let's replicate the previous "
"steps but\n"
"                this time, without confirming the order (just saving it as "
"draft)."
msgstr ""
"Anda kini tahu cara membuat pesanan baru.<br/>Mari ulangi langkah-langkah "
"sebelumnya,\n"
"                tapi kali ini tanpa mengonfirmasi pesanan (hanya "
"menyimpannya sebagai draft)."

#. module: campsite
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:campsite.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"You should be able to execute the following flows to have an overview of "
"various flows\n"
"            you can quickly execute with this package using Odoo."
msgstr ""
"Anda dapat menjalankan alur-alur berikut untuk melihat gambaran tentang "
"berbagai proses\n"
"            yang dapat dengan cepat dijalankan menggunakan paket ini di Odoo."

#. module: campsite
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:campsite.welcome_article_body
msgid "You welcome your first guests, awesome!"
msgstr "Anda sudah menyambut tamu pertama. Keren!"

#. module: campsite
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:campsite.welcome_article_body
msgid "You're now waiting for your guest to arrive."
msgstr "Anda sekarang sedang menunggu tamu tiba."

#. module: campsite
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:campsite.homepage
msgid ""
"Your Dynamic Snippet will be displayed here... This message is displayed "
"because you did not provide both a filter and a template to use.<br/>"
msgstr ""
"Snippet Dinamis Anda akan ditampilkan di sini... Pesan ini ditampilkan "
"karena Anda tidak menyediakan filter dan templat untuk digunakan.<br/>"

